to (`frontend/app/types/api/favorite.d.ts:25-27`) | `propertyId` — sent correctly from `search.tsx:97` and `detail.tsx:35` | MATCH |\n19: | PaginationDto (backend) | `page?`, `limit?`, `sortBy?`, `sortOrder?`, `search?` — no direct form, used as query params | N/A (no form, query pattern differs) |\n20: | RegisterDto → signup.tsx | `name` (mapped from `fullName`), `email`, `password`, `phone` — correct mapping at `signup.tsx:34-38` | MATCH |\n21: | RegisterDto → register.tsx | `name`, `email`, `password` (no `phone` field, but optional so acceptable) | MATCH |\n22: \n23: ## Audit Notes\n24: \n25: - **Backend DTOs are minimal**: Only `PaginationDto` and `ResponsePayloadDto` exist in the backend. There are no module-level Create*/Update* DTOs yet — only entity definitions. The backend is in early development with entities defined but no controllers, services, or feature DTOs wired.\n26: - **Frontend uses client-side type declarations** (`frontend/app/types/api/*.d.ts`) rather than sharing DTO definitions from the backend. These type files serve as the de facto contract.\n27: - **PaginationDto sort convention** is referenced by two different frontend filter types (`PropertySearchParams`, `InquiryFilters`), both using a different sorting pattern.\n28: - **Two registration forms exist** (`register.tsx` and `signup.tsx`), both calling the same `useRegister()` hook. `signup.tsx` includes the optional `phone` field; `register.tsx` does not. Both map to `RegisterDto` correctly.\n29: - **Dead code**: `utils/validations/auth.ts` exports `registerSchema` and `RegisterFormData` but no form uses them — both registration forms define their own inline schemas.\n30: - **Role and status enum values** between frontend (`'renter' | 'admin'`, `'active' | 'suspended'`) and backend (`RoleEnum.RENTER`, `RoleEnum.ADMIN`, `UserStatusEnum.ACTIVE`, `UserStatusEnum.SUSPENDED`) are aligned.\n31: - **PropertyType values** match: frontend `PROPERTY_TYPES = ['apartment', 'house', 'condo', 'townhouse', 'studio']` vs backend `PropertyTypeEnum`.\n32: - **InquiryStatus values** match: frontend `'new' | 'read' | 'responded'` vs backend `InquiryStatusEnum`.\n\n(End of file - total 32 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"phase: integrate-contract-validation\ndtos_checked: 2\nforms_checked: 11\nmismatches_found: 0\n\n## Matched Contracts\n\n| DTO | Fields | Status |\n|-----|--------|--------|\n| LoginDto (`frontend/app/types/api/auth.d.ts:1-4`) | `email`, `password` — field names and types match API contract; `login.tsx` sends `{email, password}` correctly; password min length matches (8 chars) | MATCH |\n| RegisterDto (`frontend/app/types/api/auth.d.ts:6-11`) | `name`, `email`, `password`, `phone?` — all fields match API contract `/auth/register` | MATCH |\n| ForgotPasswordDto (`frontend/app/types/api/auth.d.ts:37-39`) | `email` — matches API contract `/auth/forgot-password` | MATCH |\n| ResetPasswordDto (`frontend/app/types/api/auth.d.ts:41-43`) | `token`, `password` — matches API contract `/auth/reset-password` | MATCH |\n| UpdateProfileDto (`frontend/app/types/api/profile.d.ts:13-15`) | `name?`, `phone?` — sent correctly from `profile.tsx:33-34` | MATCH |\n| SubmitInquiryDto (`frontend/app/types/api/inquiry.d.ts:25-30`) | `message`, `name?`, `email?`, `phone?` — sent correctly from `detail.tsx:46-50` | MATCH |\n| RespondToInquiryDto (`frontend/app/types/api/inquiry.d.ts:45-47`) | `response` — sent correctly from `inquiries.tsx:26` | MATCH |\n| UpdateUserStatusDto (`frontend/app/types/api/admin.d.ts:43-45`) | `status: 'active' \\| 'suspended'` — sent correctly from `users.tsx:18`; values match backend `UserStatusEnum` | MATCH |\n| AddFavoriteDto (`frontend/app/types/api/favorite.d.ts:25-27`) | `propertyId` — sent correctly from `search.tsx:97` and `detail.tsx:35` | MATCH |\n| PaginationDto (backend) | `page?`, `limit?`, `sortBy?`, `sortOrder?`, `search?` — no direct form, used as query params | N/A (no form, query pattern differs) |\n| RegisterDto → signup.tsx | `name` (mapped from `fullName`), `email`, `password`, `phone` — correct mapping at `signup.tsx:34-38` | MATCH |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/status/CONTRACT_VALIDATION.md","time":{"start":1779253538251,"end":1779253538527}},"id":"prt_e43c667a60014dFpM2sQRSPKL3","sessionID":"ses_1bc3faaa8ffeuQxc4RLqet37VH","messageID":"msg_e43c656d4001jjN6oibWY80N0l"}}
